I personally view EP's as a split up NToV.  You have to farm the hell out of the limited named available to equip your guild.  Although I dont know much about PoTime or the Rathe yet (not to that point yet) I do feel that is was a huge mistake to make a event that requires 72 people.  There is no event in this game that should require more than 50 people IMO.  50 people seems to be the normal size of any raiding guild, so why in the hell would anyone conceive of this idea.  Unfortunatly, unless this even changes, all this event will lead to is either high end guilds recruiting ...again... or merging, or even cooperating (wont happen, why would anyone want more competition in a zone.) <p>Ralandar Jermzisghey<br>
